## ðŸ“Œ Project Overview
SmartContactHub is a system-native UX proposal that replaces fragmented communication with a unified relationship management experience. Instead of relying on scattered third-party apps and notification chaos, this concept embeds a contact-first productivity layer directly into the smartphone OS.

## ðŸ”§ Key Features
- **Unified Call & Message Log** (Phone, WhatsApp, Skype, etc.)
- **IQ Tab**: Intelligent Notification Filtering by intent
- **CRM Tab**: Light CRM to track high-value relationships
- **Microinteractions**: Emojis, reactions, and reminders from the dialer
- **Contextual Tabs**: Separate views for Recents, Connections, and CRM

